snippet.title: Dirt Track Devils - PlayStation 2 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Also known as "Simple 2000 Series Vol. 11: The Offroad Buggy". If you still have a PS3 and a UK/EU PlayStation Network account, the game is still available to download as it was part of the PS2 Classics line.

Dirt Track Devils (C) D3 Publisher
Published in PAL regions by Midas Interactive Entertainment
Developed by Vingt-et-un Systems

Captured via PCSX2
